OL,3,CThe London boroughs getting more cash
OL,4,Cfor an al fresco summer
OL,6,FThirteen London boroughs are getting
OL,7,Fextra money to help people make the
OL,8,Fmost of the summer weather.
OL,10,FProjects in Barking & Dagenham, Brent,
OL,11,FGreenwich and Lambeth have each been
OL,12,Fgiven up to #100,000 to transform
OL,13,Fareas with outdoor dining, World Cup
OL,14,Fscreenings, markets and cultural
OL,15,Factivities.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
