PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782757108
OL,3,CThe London boroughs getting more cash
OL,4,Cfor an al fresco summer
OL,6,FEleven smaller schemes in Brent,
OL,7,FCamden, Ealing, Haringey, Hounslow,
OL,8,FIslington, Lewisham, Newham, Sutton
OL,9,Fand Waltham Forest have received up to
OL,10,F#10,000 each for food and drink night
OL,11,Fmarkets, Summer Sessions featuring DJs
OL,12,Fand live music performances, and
OL,13,Ffamily-friendly community events.
OL,15,FMayor of London, Sadiq Khan, said:
OL,16,F"I'm delighted that we're working with
OL,17,Fboroughs and local businesses to bring
OL,18,Fal fresco dining, live music, events
OL,19,Fand later opening hours to streets
OL,20,Facross our capital.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782757108
OL,3,CThe London boroughs getting more cash
OL,4,Cfor an al fresco summer
OL,6,F"From Woolwich to Willesden Green,
OL,7,FFinsbury Park to Feltham, and right in
OL,8,Fthe heart of the capital in Waterloo,
OL,9,Fthis investment will create new
OL,10,Foutdoor spaces, support local
OL,11,Fbusinesses and give Londoners and
OL,12,Fvisitors even more reasons to get out
OL,13,Fand enjoy our city.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782757108
OL,3,CThe London boroughs getting more cash
OL,4,Cfor an al fresco summer
OL,6,F"Today also marks a landmark moment
OL,7,Ffor London's licensing system as for
OL,8,Fthe first time ever City Hall has a
OL,9,Fdirect say in how licensing decisions
OL,10,Fare made across the capital. By making
OL,11,Fit easier to extend opening hours and
OL,12,Fexpand what's on offer, I'm determined
OL,13,Fto support our hospitality and
OL,14,Fnightlife, as we build a better London
OL,15,Ffor everyone."
OL,17,FKate Nicholls, Chair of UKHospitality,
OL,18,Fadded: "It's fantastic to see so many
OL,19,FLondon boroughs taking advantage of
OL,20,Fthe Mayor's Summer Streets fund.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
