CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782757108
OL,3,CThe London boroughs getting more cash
OL,4,Cfor an al fresco summer
OL,6,F"From food markets and al fresco
OL,7,Fdining to World Cup screenings, it
OL,8,Fshows the power of hospitality to
OL,9,Fdrive activity and bring our
OL,10,Fcommunities together. I look forward
OL,11,Fto seeing the success of all the
OL,12,Fevents this summer."
